          "IMPERATIVE = commands, advice, urging.",
          "Italian has THREE forms: tu, voi, Lei.",
          "",
          "REGULAR FORMATION:",
          "",
          "              -ARE    -ERE    -IRE",
          "   tu         -a      -i      -i",
          "   voi        -ate    -ete    -ite",
          "   Lei        -i      -a      -a",
          "",
          "EXAMPLES:",
          "",
          "   parla!    = speak! (tu)",
          "   parlate!  = speak! (voi)",
          "   parli!    = speak (Lei, formal)",
          "   finisci!  = finish! (-isc- verbs)",
          "",
          "The Lei form uses SUBJUNCTIVE endings."
